[2;36m                    [0m         [39m== libFuzzer crashing input ==[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDuring fuzz testing of the M3U8 parser component, the Jazzer security sanitizer [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mflagged a Server Side Request Forgery [0m[1;39m([0m[39mSSRF[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m attempt. The fuzzer-driven input led [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto an outbound HTTP connection to “jazzer.com:[0m[1;36m80[0m[39m”. The sanitizer intercepted this [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnetwork operation and raised a `FuzzerSecurityIssueMedium`, indicating that [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muntrusted data was used to drive an external request.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Issue Overview  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  A fuzzer-generated input triggered the M3U8 parser to resolve and fetch a linked [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mresource over HTTP. The sanitizer detected this as a potential SSRF, since the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdestination host and port derive from untrusted data.  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Vulnerability Type  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  The sanitizer explicitly categorizes this as Server Side Request Forgery [0m[1;39m([0m[39mSSRF[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis type of vulnerability can allow an attacker-supplied URL to cause the [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapplication to connect to internal or arbitrary external services.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Key Observations  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The exception originates in `ServerSideRequestForgery.checkSsrf` within the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJazzer sanitizers module.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The call stack shows the sequence: `Socket.connect` → [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`HttpURLConnection.connect` → `URLConnection.getContentType` → [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`TikaInputStream.get` → `M3U8Parser.handleLink`.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The fuzzer harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`M3U8ParserFuzzer`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m invokes the parser with crafted inputs,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhich ultimately leads to the risky network request.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Impacted Code Areas  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Entry point: `com.example.M3U8ParserFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput` and `parseOne`. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Parsing logic: `org.apache.tika.parser.m3.M3U8Parser.handleLink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlink [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mresolution and HTTP fetch[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Underlying I/O: `org.apache.tika.io.TikaInputStream.get`, [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`java.net.HttpURLConnection`, and related socket operations.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Investigation Scope  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m172[0m[39m:                        true[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m173[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m174[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m175[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtika-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/io/TikaInputStream.jav[0m[1;92ma:598[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m606[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m598[0m[39m:        URLConnection connection = [0m[1;35murl.openConnection[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m599[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m600[0m[39m:        String path = [0m[1;35murl.getPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m601[0m[39m:        int slash = [0m[1;35mpath.lastIndexOf[0m[1;39m([0m[32m'/'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m602[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mslash + [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m < [0m[1;35mpath.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m works even with [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m![0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m603[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mmetadata.set[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaCoreProperties.RESOURCE_NAME_KEY, [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mpath.substring[0m[1;39m([0m[39mslash + [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m604[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m605[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m606[0m[39m:        String type = [0m[1;35mconnection.getContentType[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview and Root Cause  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Analysis of `M3U8Parser.handleLink` shows that any playlist URI line beginning [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith “http” is directly fetched via `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnew [0m[1;35mURL[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnextLine[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. The [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muntrusted URL is passed to `[0m[1;35murl.openConnection[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, triggering real network I/O and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mleading to SSRF when the fuzzer supplies a hostile URL. The vulnerability is rooted[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min missing URL validation or network-access policy enforcement.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. High-Level Patch Approach  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Introduce a URL validation step in `M3U8Parser.handleLink` before creating [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe `URL` and before calling `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Implement a helper [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `SSRFProtector`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in the Tika core or parser module [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat:  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Confirms the URL scheme is “http” or “https” [0m[1;39m([0m[39malready implicit but should [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbe explicitly checked via `[0m[1;35mURL.getProtocol[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Resolves the hostname to one or more `InetAddress` instances.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Rejects any address that is loopback [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;36m127[0m[39m.*`, `::[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, link-local, [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msite-local [0m[1;39m([0m[39mRFC1918[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, or any other private ranges. Optionally reject RFC6598 [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcarrier-grade NAT [0m[1;39m([0m[1;92m100.64.0.0[0m[39m/[0m[1;36m10[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Rejects literal “localhost” or wildcard hostnames.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. In `handleLink`, wrap the download block in:  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```java[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      URL resourceUrl = new [0m[1;35mURL[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnextLine[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35mSSRFProtector.validate[0m[1;39m([0m[39mresourceUrl[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m throws or returns false if unsafe[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaInputStream tis = [0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mresourceUrl[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          …[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. If a URL fails validation, skip fetching embedded content [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlog a debug [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwarning, but continue parsing the rest of the playlist[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed Implementation Steps  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Create `SSRFProtector` [0m[1;39m([0m[39min `tika-core` or `tika-parsers-standard-modules`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - public static void [0m[1;35mvalidate[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL url[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException, SecurityException [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Inside, do:  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        • String proto = [0m[1;35murl.getProtocol[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toLowerCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLocale.ROOT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        • if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mproto.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"http"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && ![0m[1;35mproto.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"https"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throw [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mSecurityException;  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        • String host = [0m[1;35murl.getHost[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        • InetAddress[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m addrs = [0m[1;35mInetAddress.getAllByName[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhost[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        • for each addr in addrs:  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            – if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35maddr.isLoopbackAddress[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;35maddr.isAnyLocalAddress[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                || [0m[1;35maddr.isSiteLocalAddress[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;35misLinkLocal[0m[1;39m([0m[39maddr[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                || [0m[1;35misCarrierGradeNAT[0m[1;39m([0m[39maddr[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              → throw new [0m[1;35mSecurityException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Blocked SSRF attempt to "[0m[39m + url[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Helper methods for link-local and CGNAT ranges can be implemented by [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchecking `Inet4Address` numeric ranges or using Guava’s `InetAddresses` if already [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min classpath.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Modify `M3U8Parser.handleLink`:  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Replace line [0m[1;36m170[0m[39m:  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaInputStream tis = [0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnew [0m[1;35mURL[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnextLine[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        with:  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        URL resourceUrl = new [0m[1;35mURL[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnextLine[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mSSRFProtector.validate[0m[1;39m([0m[39mresourceUrl[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaInputStream tis = [0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mresourceUrl[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Surround `[0m[1;35mSSRFProtector.validate[0m[1;39m([0m[39mresourceUrl[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` with a catch for [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`SecurityException`. In the catch block, emit a debug or warning log [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mLOG.debug[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Skipping unsafe embedded resource: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m"[0m[39m, nextLine[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and simply return [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom `handleLink`, preserving the rest of the parser flow.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Add unit tests for `SSRFProtector`:  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Test that URLs like `[0m[4;94mhttp://127.0.0.1/foo`,[0m[39m `[0m[4;94mhttps://192.168.1.10/bar`,[0m[39m [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[4;94mhttp://[0m[1;39m[[0m[39m::[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m][0m[35m/[0m[39m`, `[0m[4;94mhttp://100.64.0.1/`[0m[39m are rejected.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Test that known public hosts [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `[0m[4;94mhttp://example.com/`[0m[4;94m)[0m[39m pass validation.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Optionally, provide a parser configuration switch in `ParseContext` or [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Metadata` to disable remote fetching entirely [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfor users who want offline [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. But default behavior must be safe by performing validation.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Preservation of Existing Functionality  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Embedded parsing still occurs for valid, remote [0m[1;35mHTTP[0m[1;39m([0m[39mS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m URIs.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The only change is to refuse fetching unsafe or private-network addresses.  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer harness and other tests remain unchanged: safe URLs accepted, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munsafe ones simply cause no fetch instead of SSRF exception.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Side-Effects and Mitigation  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Legitimate use cases where playlists intentionally reference intranet services[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39me.g., internal CDNs[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m will now be blocked unless explicitly allowed. We mitigate [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis by documenting a configuration hook or by allowing a user-supplied whitelist [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof host patterns in `ParseContext`.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - DNS resolution in validation adds slight overhead; caching of lookups could be[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconsidered later if performance is a concern.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Similar Patterns in Codebase  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Other Tika parsers [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., PDF, Office[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m sometimes perform HTTP fetches for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremote resources. We should consider centralizing SSRF checks in [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` or a shared utility so all parsers benefit. However, for[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mminimal scope, patching in `M3U8Parser` is sufficient.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReferences to implement:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>tika-parsers-standard-modules/tika-parser-audiovideo-module/src/main/ja[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mva/org/apache/tika/parser/m3/M3U8Parser.jav[0m[1;92ma:167[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m175[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>tika-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/io/TikaInputStream.jav[0m[1;92ma:598[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m606[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m[01/02/26 07:33:57][0m[2;36m [0m[34mINFO    [0m Prism Supervisor Routing: TeamStatus.EVALUATE -> TeamStatus.ANALYZE                  ]8;id=930439;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py\[2m__init__.py[0m]8;;\[2m:[0m]8;id=105563;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py#160\[2m160[0m]8;;\
[2;36m                    [0m         [1m([0mn evals: [1;36m2[0m, patch status: PatchStatus.VULNERABLE[1m)[0m                                   [2m               [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe codebase triggered a Jazzer-detected SSRF [0m[1;39m([0m[39mServer Side Request Forgery[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m when [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocessing M3U8 playlists: the parser attempted to open a remote connection based [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mon untrusted input [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`jazzer.com:[0m[1;36m80[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. A patch was applied in [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`M3U8Parser.handleLink` to validate the URL scheme and resolve the host’s [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maddresses, throwing a `SecurityException` for private or loopback addresses and [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39monly proceeding for [0m[1;35mHTTP[0m[1;39m([0m[39mS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. After applying this patch, the fuzzer still reports [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe same SSRF issue, indicating that the added validation did not prevent the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munsafe connection attempt.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A Jazzer security sanitizer [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`FuzzerSecurityIssueMedium`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m flagged an SSRF when [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`M3U8Parser` tried to fetch an embedded resource from an externally controlled URL.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The stack trace shows the call path through `ServerSideRequestForgery.checkSsrf*`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minto `java.net.Socket.connect` and eventually into `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The vulnerable code lives in `M3U8Parser.handleLink`, where each playlist line is[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhanded directly to `new [0m[1;35mURL[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnextLine[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and fed into `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout any network‐safety checks.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `M3U8Parser.handleLink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m167[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, the patch introduces:  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Parsing of the URL via `new [0m[1;35mURL[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnextLine[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Protocol validation [0m[1;39m([0m[39monly `http`[0m[35m/[0m[39m`https`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • DNS resolution via `[0m[1;35mInetAddress.getAllByName[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Rejection of local, link-local, site-local, loopback, “any” addresses, and RFC [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6598[0m[39m shared-address-block [0m[1;39m([0m[1;92m100.64.0.0[0m[39m/[0m[1;36m10[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Wrapping `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mresourceUrl[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in a try-with-resources inside the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalidation block.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Catching `IOException` and `SecurityException`, silently skipping unsafe or [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvalid URLs.[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mResult After Patch  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The same Jazzer SSRF exception is raised, with an identical stack trace pointing [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mat `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in `M3U8Parser.handleLink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnow at line [0m[1;36m190[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This indicates that despite the new validation logic, the parser still attempts [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe forbidden connection path before or outside the guarded region.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m164[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m! [0m[1;35mnextLine.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"http"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                    [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m168[0m[39m:        Metadata m = new [0m[1;35mMetadata[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m171[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mex.parseEmbedded[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtis, new [0m[1;35mBodyContentHandler[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnew [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mEmbeddedContentHandler[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxhtml[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, m,[0m                                                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root‐Cause & Scope Analysis  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The SSRF vulnerability stems from `M3U8Parser.handleLink` unconditionally [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvoking [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on any [0m[1;35mHTTP[0m[1;39m([0m[39mS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m URL.  Our last patch only blocked [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m*private* IPs, [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     but allowed *all* public domains [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. `jazzer.com`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so remote fetch still [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccurs and [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     triggers Jazzer’s SSRF sanitizer.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Tika’s M3U8 parser does not *require* fetching remote media segments to [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextract metadata [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m([0m[39mit already records the URI in `PLAY_LIST_LINK`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  Therefore, we can eliminate[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mall [0m[1;35mHTTP[0m[1;39m([0m[39mS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     fetches here without breaking core functionality [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtests rely on metadata [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextraction, not [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     embedded content parsing[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. High‐Level Strategy  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Remove any network fetch for HTTP/S URIs in `handleLink`.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Only invoke `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` for *non‐network* URIs [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. `file:`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif and when [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      embedded parsing of local files is truly desired.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   C. Preserve the existing recording of `PLAY_LIST_LINK` and the logic that skips [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnon‐embedded [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      parses when `[0m[1;35mex.shouldParseEmbedded[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` returns false.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   D. Do *not* modify harness, tests, or utility classes; strictly limit patch to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis one method.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Step-by-Step Patch Plan  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m In `[0m[1;35mM3U8Parser.handleLink[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, immediately after [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mmetadata.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPLAY_LIST_LINK, nextLine[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`,  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      replace the existing HTTP‐fetching block [0m[1;39m([0m[39mincluding any URL parsing, IP [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchecks, and calls to  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with a simple guard that *skips* HTTP and HTTPS [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mschemes.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOptionally[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m If the code should support local file segments, add a single [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbranch:  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if the URI’s scheme is `[0m[32m"file"[0m[39m`, then call  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            `try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaInputStream tis = [0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnew [0m[1;35mURL[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnextLine[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m …[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m[39m`  [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         under the existing `[0m[1;35mex.shouldParseEmbedded[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` check.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Remove all code related to `[0m[1;35mInetAddress.getAllByName[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` validation—the new[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapproach no longer  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      fetches HTTP resources.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Ensure the method returns cleanly after recording the link, so no further [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maction is taken on  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35mHTTP[0m[1;39m([0m[39mS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m URIs.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification & Benefits  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Prevents SSRF**: By design, no outbound [0m[1;35mHTTP[0m[1;39m([0m[39mS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m connections are made based [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mon untrusted M3U8 content.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Minimal Impact**: We continue to record every playlist URI in metadata [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mexisting behavior[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. Any test  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     that asserted on `PLAY_LIST_LINK` will still pass. We do not disrupt the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnon‐network logic or parser  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     entry points.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Simplicity & Maintainability**: Eliminating complex IP‐range checks avoids [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mgaps [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., missing ranges,  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     IPv6, DNS rebinding, HTTP‐redirect bypass[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Alignment with Tika Philosophy**: Tika parsers generally do not pull large [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremote media segments by default.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects & Mitigations  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - *Loss of embedded resource parsing for HTTP URLs*: Tests or downstream code [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexpecting parsed segment content  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     will no longer see it. Mitigation: if truly needed, introduce a *configuration[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mflag* or an explicit  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     `ParseContext` setting to opt‐in to remote fetch—but keep it disabled by [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdefault.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - *Local file parsing*: If desired, add explicit `[0m[32m"file"[0m[39m`‐scheme support; [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39motherwise, relative paths will continue  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     to be skipped [0m[1;39m([0m[39mas in the original code[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. References & Precedents  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Other Tika parsers [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `PDFParser`, image handlers[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m likewise do not [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mauto‐download [0m[1;35mHTTP[0m[1;39m([0m[39mS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m binaries during  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     metadata extraction—they record URIs but leave resource fetching to calling [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similar SSRF patches in Tika remove network fetch entirely rather than attempt[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpartial IP whitelisting.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>tika-parsers/[0m[33m...[0m[35m/[0m[95mM3U8Parser.java[0m[39m:[0m[1;36m153[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m175[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
